&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience with Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Access)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills that include advanced analytical and reasoning abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstration of ability to apply actuarial principles to complex situations&lt;/li&gt;
