&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Annuity Reinsurance Administration Analyst is responsible for performing various duties to ensure accurate and timely reporting with annuity reinsurers. This includes preparing journal entries and required settlement reporting for annuity reinsurance treaties and having a thorough understanding of the treaties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position reports to the Manager, Annuity Reinsurance Accounting &amp;amp; Administration.&lt;/p&gt;
