&lt;li&gt;Bachelors degree in Human Resources, Business, Finance, or related field, or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of progressive experience in compensation analysis, program design, and administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Preferred&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
