&lt;li&gt;Improve operational efficiency within cash management, portfolio reporting, and data processes through automation and process redesign.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, investigate, and resolve data inconsistencies or errors across investment systems and reports.&lt;/li&gt;
