&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Product Owner will be responsible for defining, prioritizing, and delivering solutions that enhance operational efficiency and customer experience across complex technologies. This role will serve as the voice of the business, translating strategy and operational needs into actionable requirements, and ensuring that technology solutions deliver measurable value. The Product Owner will collaborate with cross-functional teams, vendors, and IT partners to manage the product backlog, oversee BAU (business-as-usual) enhancements, and drive continuous improvement. This position requires strong leadership, business acumen, and the ability to balance strategic vision with tactical execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
