&lt;li&gt;Own and prioritize the product backlog, translating business needs into well-defined epics, user stories, and acceptance criteria that deliver measurable business value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive consensus and collaboration by acting as the primary liaison between business stakeholders and development teams to understand business context, gather requirements, and communicate product plans and progress&lt;/li&gt;
