&lt;li&gt;Measure and report on product success, conducting post-implementation analysis against expected business outcomes and providing transparent status updates to leaders and stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee product budget and resource allocation for managed applications, ensuring efficient use of operating budget&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive continuous improvement by challenging existing processes, promoting Agile best practices, and mentoring teams on digital tools and methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
