&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is a senior level position performing various duties related to the financial reporting process for Fidelity &amp;amp; Guaranty Life and subsidiaries. Areas of responsibility include preparation of the quarterly and annual Statutory financial statements, footnote disclosures, and analysis required for Statutory reporting. This position will also support the department with respect to internal and external audit requests.&lt;/p&gt;
